data.description: Backup Offers Welcome. CREDIT OF $10,000.00 TO BUYER. Beverly Hills Style Barndominium. This is a 3 to 4 Bedroom home where one Bedroom can be used as a Home Office. 3-level home where the 1.5 level can be used as a game room or the Formal Dining Area. Home has been designed for Work or Relaxation that starts as soon as you walk up to the front door waterfall that continues across to the back with a tanning pool view from the primary bedroom and family room. An Amazing feature is the 2-story primary closet with its own private balcony and built-in desk for a private study area/Den. Other features: tankless water heater, energy-efficient appliances & lighting, Pine cabinetry built onsite, vertical cable & cedar railing, stylish wall accents and fixtures, granite and quartz countertops, Farmhouse sink, Alarm System, Ring Doorbell, Nest and so much more. Garage Designed for 1 RV & 1 car pass-thru garage with an Industrial Size Garage door & a 32' square ft elevator storage/workbench.
